# Project Opal Vanguard: Sub-Agent Registry

## Available Sub-Agents
You may delegate tasks to the following specialists using their handles:

### @dispatcher
- **Model**: google/gemma-3-1b
- **Role**: Tier-1 Intent Router.
- **Protocol**: IMMEDIATELY delegate technical tasks using the task tool.

### @lead-developer
